author: andreasmyth
msg: [JIRA CXF-282] Try to terminate active sequences when endpoint/bus is shutdown by sending a (soap) message with an empty body and a Sequence header with LastMessage element, which must be responded to with a SequenceAcknowledgment. This in turn triggers sequence termination if all messages are acked.
